Package pusty.f0i.inst

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Inst
    Instruction class, all instructions extend from this
    Inst000DEBUG
    Prints out content from parameter 1
    Inst005ADD
    Adds Parameter 1 and Parameter 2 and puts it into Parameter 1 (also updates flags)
    Inst007AND
    Ands Logical and Parameter 1 and Parameter 2 and updates Zero Flag (resets other flags)
    Inst017CALL
    Jumps to Parameter 1 and adds the current line to the stack
    Inst018CBW
    Converts AL to AX
    Inst025CMP
    Subtracts Parameter 1 and Parameter 2 and updates flags
    Inst026CMPS
    Subtracts EDI and ESI and updates flags and then increases EDI and ESI
    Inst032DEC
    Decreases Parameter 1 by 1 and puts it into Parameter 1 and then updates the flags
    Inst033DIV
    Divides AX/Parameter 1 and puts puts AX/Parameter 1 into AL and AX%Parameter 1 into AL (for size = byte)
    Inst037HLT
    Halts the system
    Inst040IN
    Inputs Bios.readIn(int) for Parameter 2 and then puts it into Parameter 1
    Inst041INC
    Increases Parameter 1 by 1 and puts it into Parameter 1
    Inst043INT
    Calls Interrupt Parameter 1 at the Bios.emulateBios(pusty.f0i.interpreter.MemoryMap, int)
    Inst047IRET
    Pops one byte from stack and jumps to it
    Inst048JA
    Jump to Parameter 1 if above
    Inst049JAE
    Jump to Parameter 1 if above or equals
    Inst050JB
    Jump to Parameter 1 if below
    Inst051JBE
    Jump to Parameter 1 if above or equals
    Inst052JC
    Jump to Parameter 1 if carry flag is set
    Inst053JCXZ
    Jump to Parameter 1 if CX is 0
    Inst053JECXZ
    Jump to Parameter 1 if ECX is 0
    Inst054JE
    Jump to Parameter 1 if equals
    Inst055JG
    Jump to Parameter 1 if greater
    Inst056JGE
    Jump to Parameter 1 if greater equals
    Inst057JL
    Jump to Parameter 1 if less
    Inst058JLE
    Jump to Parameter 1 if less equals
    Inst059JMP
    Jump to Parameter 1 if Parameter 1 is a NODE type.
    Inst060JNC
    Jump to Parameter 1 if the carry flag isn't set
    Inst061JNE
    Jump to Parameter 1 if not equals
    Inst062JNO
    Jump to Parameter 1 if Overflow isn't set
    Inst063JNS
    Jump to Parameter 1 if Signed isn't set
    Inst065JO
    Jump to Parameter 1 if Overflow is set
    Inst067JS
    Jump to Parameter 1 if signed is set
    Inst071LEA
    Copies the address of Parameter 2 to Parameter 1
    Inst081LODS
    Load content from esi to al and increase esi by 1 (byte)
    Inst082LOOP
    Decreases cx by one and if it's zero do nothing and if not jump to Parameter 1
    Inst088MOV
    Copies Parameter 2 to Parameter 1
    Inst089MOVS
    Copy content from esi to edi and increase both
    Inst092MUL
    Multiplies Parameter 1 by AL and puts it into AX (byte)
    Inst093NEG
    Switches sign from Parameter 1 and puts it into Parameter 1
    Inst094NOP
    Does nothing
    Inst095NOT
    Logical not Parameter 1 and put it into Parameter 1 (also updates flags)
    Inst096OR
    Logical Ors Parameter 1 and Parameter 2 and puts it into Parameter 1 (also updates flags)
    Inst097OUT
    Writes Parameter 2 at Bios.writeOut(int, int) with Parameter 1
    Inst099POP
    Removes 1 Argument from stack and puts it into Argument 1
    Inst100POPA
    Removes all word registers from stack and puts them accordingly
    Inst100POPAD
    Removes all dword registers from stack and puts them accordingly
    Inst102PUSH
    Pushes Argument 1 to the stack
    Inst103PUSHA
    Pushes all word registers to the stack
    Inst103PUSHAD
    Pushes all dword registers to the stack
    Inst110RET
    Pops one byte from stack and jumps to it
    Inst114SHL
    Shifts Parameter 1 Parameter 2 bits to the left (and Carry to the last outshifted bit)
    Inst137SHR
    Shifts Parameter 1 Parameter 2 bits to the right (and Carry to the last outshifted bit)
    Inst144STOS
    Copies the content from AL to EDI and increases EDI by 1 (byte)
    Inst146SUB
    Subtracts Parameter 1 by Parameter 2 and puts it into Parameter 1 and updates flags
    Inst147TEST
    Logical ANDs Parameter 1 and Parameter 2 and updates flags
    Inst154XOR
    Logical XORs Parameter 1 and Parameter 2 and puts the result into Parameter 1
